Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.79,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:46.28,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:46.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我們的願望實現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.09,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fs48}戰場女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.74,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:06.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:06.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隱藏的傷痕在發冷顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.55,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找尋我的容身之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:18.82,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:18.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在這個遵循常識的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:23.34,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:23.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破無可救藥的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.59,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:35.21,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:35.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封閉的心靈正發出吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:42.57,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:42.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.27,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.27,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我們幾乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.52,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要曖昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.77,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}只需去追尋真切的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧第七小隊護送我平安返回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時在城中休息 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就此告退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金先生 這也是艾麗西婭的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請理解她的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問這樣就滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 艾麗西婭的離開我們每個人都有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻在這裡受艾麗西婭的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她此時此刻也在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 被對方的女武神壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶豫什麼 吉蘭達約近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何應對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是怪物 遇上同類就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍 第三第五坦克中隊失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼 快把部隊撤到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全…到底哪裡是安全所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在為什麼而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有了歸宿 沒有要保護的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼忘我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很早以前就認識她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識的艾麗西婭·梅爾姬沃特已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 即便如此我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了 當時的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼忘我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是那裡出身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫艾麗西婭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪聽起來耳熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你也在那間收容所呆過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在老交情上勸你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥時不要帶有多餘的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是敵人的計謀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則為什麼會在這時…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍加利亞方面軍總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安·蓋倫斯本·雷金萊布親自前來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求締結停戰協議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向來是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦電波與Ragnite反應值都超過基準值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等級28 優秀的數值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他候選者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法遣散 這裡對外的形象是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向孤兒伸出援手的慈善設施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A1號的轉移手續拜託了 盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑幾次才肯罷休 只有這裡會收留你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來A1號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎A1號 只要你還是女武神的後裔實驗就會繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家彼此之間該如何相處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該懂點事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不識好歹 隨你便吧 但你的未來不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨過這個世界 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 A1號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅一次邂逅改變了我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A1號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞 是這種花的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效力於吾 伴隨吾身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敵人的主力全部交給賽爾貝莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將去和加利亞說悄悄話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是佯動作戰 沒想到能如此輕易接近蘭蒂格瑞絲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也顧不過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有抵抗結果也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心也沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,締結這份協議絕不會讓你們後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你口中的停戰到底是何含義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如字面上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:12:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為結束這場令百姓受苦\N並可能毀滅加利亞一切的消耗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰局正傾向我方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續打下去的話我們將贏得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們為何在此交談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼選擇這個時間點上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞的國民們確實飽受這場戰爭的煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非我本願
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說出你的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭蒂格瑞絲城的無血開城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亞 成為吾的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便締結政治婚姻也不可能讓民眾忘記這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事自不用說 多此一言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是繼承加利亞的王位 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這種事 發起這場戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你稱其為「這種事」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何其迂腐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要擁有王位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要擁有蘭蒂格瑞絲王族中 女武神的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味著擁有了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用身陷帝國的權力鬥爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠建立起吾心目中的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是女武神族的後裔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 我一直在考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望什麼 怎麼樣才能為你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今後要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 背著這麼大包行李
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都猜得出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷跑可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也別想甩下我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話 你們也會上軍事法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 我們已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我必須去向艾麗西婭道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這樣下去絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭是不是女武神人沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 今後我會按自己的意願行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在…想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她擁有 但是我卻沒有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰鬥理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有輸不起的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這種力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接下來的一擊中分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等什麼 殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有要保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能那樣堅強地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我想起自己也有寶貴的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太心軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然輸給這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活著就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金這麼說過 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗給你的瞬間 我已經沒有任何價值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著 肯定還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:18:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒為女武神人後 還能說出這種理想主義論調
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談話到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 擒住她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要貫徹我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞 你要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在我心目中重於一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 沒有死亡成就的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要公佈自己是達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭蒂格瑞絲家族的威信將歸入塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也無法再利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這虛假的歷史 到了該結束的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們已無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下來電
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 去完成其他目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和吉蘭達約以及賽爾貝莉亞上校失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 賽爾貝莉亞還有用她的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校對您那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為您而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋住吾去路的人 只此一種下場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太過悲傷的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知該說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默數著星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤獨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早該習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾獨自將你找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我願心中只思念著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不願忘卻這悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}僅此而已 唯有此心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}是的 那是唯一的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人無法一個人生存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果只會傷害別人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著究竟有何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有恐怖力量為加利亞而戰之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 戰場女武神 第二十五章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:35.00,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}製作：Casval 晶晶電腦 hawkt 小林 LBS123456 Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:38.00,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}協力：jabal taburiss 綠葉之硯 Oilon 冷たぃ海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算為保護大家…出過一份力了
